          %li If you are drafted, the Team Manager will contact you and will let you know when you can play next. The Team Manager is responsible for notifying us, that he or she has drafted a free agent.
          %br
          %li If there are not enough free agents drafted, then we will attempt to form a team with the remaining agents.

